_Balthisar Tidy_ has a very configurable display. To hide (or show) the
**Tidy Messages** panel, follow the steps below.

<div class="steps" markdown="1">

1. Select **Tidy Messages** from the **View** menu. If the panel is currently
   visible you will see that is is checked.
   ![view menu][menu-view]

2. You can confirm that the menu items is now unchecked, and the messages panel
   is hidden.

